ama papers leak reported by the miami herald and mcclatchy dc read more idaho rancher’s wife i saw them murder my husband reported by the idaho statesman read more website survey mcclatchy  markets menu our impactmarketersinvestorscareersaboutcontactemployees our impact marketspartnershipsinvestments marketersinvestorscareers view positions about communitybehind the scenesawardshistoryleadershipnews contactemployees marketspartnershipsinvestments  south caldwell streetcharlotte nc  president  publisher ann caulkins vp of advertising  kelly mirt executive editor sherry chisenhall charlotteobservercom download media kit  digital trafficavg mo unique visitors avg mo page views   print circulationdaily sunday  the charlotte observer has continued throughout its years of service to charlotte and the surrounding communities to accurately reflect the region and what matters to the local residents the observer heavily covers development and schools—factors strongly affected by rampant growth in the city and the region—and continues deep coverage of the areas traditional interests banking business industry religion and stockcar racing the paper tackles controversial economic and social issues and is innovative in creating new products such as the niche site charlotte five a publication serving young adults interested in nightlife local development culture and causes that are important to them the charlotte observer staff has won four pulitzer prizes including two gold medals for public service website survey mcclatchy  markets menu our impactmarketersinvestorscareersaboutcontactemployees our impact marketspartnershipsinvestments marketersinvestorscareers view positions about communitybehind the scenesawardshistoryleadershipnews contactemployees marketspartnershipsinvestments  w canal drivekennewick wa  president  publisher gregg mcconnell advertising director sean flaherty executive editor laurie williams tricityheraldcom download media kit  digital trafficavg mo unique visi