 publications such as the miami herald the kansas city star the sacramento bee the charlotte observer the raleigh news and observer and the fort worth startelegram the companys segments include western segment and eastern segment its western segment consists of its newspaper operations in california the northwest and the midwest the companys eastern segment consists primarily of newspaper operations in the southeast and florida the company operates  media companies in  united states markets in  states providing each of these communities with news and advertising services in a range of digital and print formatsthe companys operations include approximately  local media businesses in in over  growth markets across the united states that consist of daily newspapers websites and mobile applications mobile news and advertising video products publications direct marketing direct mail services and community newspapers its newspapers range from dailies serving metropolitan areas to nondaily newspapers serving small communities its business is divided between those media companies operated west of the mississippi river and those that are east of it but include five operating regions california the carolinas southeast midwest and northwest in addition to its media companies the company also owns over  of careerbuilder llc which operates an online job website careerbuildercom and homefinder llc which operates the online real estate website homefindercom as well as certain other digital company investments » full overview of mni company address mcclatchy co  q stsacramento   ca    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation kevin mcclatchy  craig forman  elaine lintecum  mark zieman  billie mcconkey  » more officers  directors mcclatchy co news briefmcclatchy q loss per share  jul   briefmcclatchy says kelly mirt promoted to publisher vp of advertising for the wichita eagle jul   briefmcclatchy names anjali joshi to board of directors jul   briefmcclat